snippet.title: The Real Reason Maddie Ziegler Was Abby's Favorite On Dance Moms
snippet.description:
The Truth About Why Maddy Was Abby Lee Miller's Favourite On Dance Moms 
SUBSCRIBE for more TheThings ► http://bit.ly/TheThingsSub

Dance Moms Season 8: Who The Next Maddie Ziegler Will Be ► https://youtu.be/ekG5Tjx0h6Q
The Real Reason Mackenzie Ziegler Won't Talk To Former Dance Teacher Abby Lee Miller ► https://youtu.be/ipRkJrSh6yQ

If you love drama, competition, and hilarious moments, you’re probably a huge fan of the reality TV show “Dance Moms,” and we can't say we really blame you! There's no one quite like Abby Lee Miller in this world, which is why we just can't get enough of her. But, when it comes to Abby, there's only one person she just can't get enough of, and that's Maddie Ziegler. Despite teaching hundreds of students how to dance, Maddie has always been the one who left a mark. She brought something new to the table that Abby had never seen, and it turned her into a star. 

There's a handful of reasons why Abby chose to favor Maddie over her other students, and we’re going to discuss each and every one of them. Maddie started dancing when she was just a toddler and has had a lifelong relationship with her former dance coach. Still, that doesn't explain why Maddie received special treatment from Abby. Tune into TheThings to find out how Maddie managed to climb to the top of the pyramid and stay there.
